heading: Lost Archives Dungeon Guide
content: Lost Archives is an important dungeon because this is where you complete the to unlock Sorcerer's class mechanic. While you're here, you'll want to complete the whole entire dungeon so you can pick up the Renown and the . Stock up on your Sigils for this one; you'll run it over and over again for massive hordes of loot! While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
